- ALL &quot;sleep&quot; type spells (mesmerize, stun, root) now can be cast only once per minute per target. This should alleviate some player concerns about being &quot;chain-stunned&quot;. You can still cast the spell as normal, however, it will have no effect on a player if he has had that same effect on him in the previous minute. <br>
